videos.description: Davion Mintz dribbles around the screen then lobs it up to Martin Krampelj for the nice alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Creighton's Mintz-Krampelj connection leads to  nice dunk

videos.headline: Seton Hall's Powell goes coast to coast
